snippet.title: Salaar CeaseFire Telugu Trailer | Prabhas, Prashanth, Prithviraj, Shruthi, Vijay Kiragandur |Hombale
snippet.description:
Please…I…Kindly…Request!🔥
Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

snippet.title: Thankamani | Teaser | Dileep | Ratheesh Reghunandan | Super Good Films | Saina Music | Iffaar Media
snippet.description:
Thankamani is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language crime thriller film written and directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan and Produced by R B Choudhry under the banner of Super good films in association with Iffaar Media Raaffi Mathirra. The film stars Dileep and is based on a real-life incident that occurred in Thankamany in October 1986. Thankamani Music Rights has been acquired by Saina Music.

Written & Directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan
Produced by  RB Choudary , Raaffi Mathirra
D.O.P Manoj Pillai
Editor Shyam Sasidharan
Music William Francis
Executive Producer Sujit J Nair
Sound Design Ganesh Marar-Sreejesh Nair (Mixing)
Lyrics B T Anil Kumar
Art Director Manu Jagadh
Makeup Roshan
Costume Designer Arun Manohar
Stunts Rajasekhar, Supreme Sundar, Mafia Sasi, Stun Shiva
Project Designers Sajith Krishna, Ashokan AMrutha
Production Controller Mohan (Amritha)
Project Head Sumith B P
Asso. Directors Abhijith PR, Jophin Vargheese
Colorist Liju Prabhakar
VFX Eggwhite
Stills Shalu Peyad

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. snippet.title: FURIOSA : A MAD MAX SAGA | OFFICIAL TRAILER #1
snippet.description:
This is her Odyssey. #Furiosa - Only in Theaters 2024

Anya Taylor-Joy and Chris Hemsworth star in Academy Award-winning mastermind George Miller’s “Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga,” the much-anticipated return to the iconic dystopian world he created more than 30 years ago with the seminal “Mad Max” films.  Miller now turns the page again with an all-new original, standalone action adventure that will reveal the origins of the powerhouse character from the multiple Oscar-winning global smash “Mad Max: Fury Road.”  The new feature from Warner Bros. Pictures and Village Roadshow Pictures is produced by Miller and his longtime partner, Oscar-nominated producer Doug Mitchell (“Mad Max: Fury Road,” “Babe”), under their Australian-based Kennedy Miller Mitchell banner. 

As the world fell, young Furiosa is snatched from the Green Place of Many Mothers and falls into the hands of a great Biker Horde led by the Warlord Dementus.  Sweeping through the Wasteland, they come across the Citadel presided over by The Immortan Joe.  While the two Tyrants war for dominance, Furiosa must survive many trials as she puts together the means to find her way home.

Taylor-Joy stars in the title role, and along with Hemsworth, the film also stars Alyla Browne and Tom Burke. 

Miller penned the script with “Mad Max: Fury Road” co-writer Nico Lathouris.  Miller’s behind-the-scenes creative team includes first assistant director PJ Voeten and second unit director and stunt coordinator Guy Norris, director of photography Simon Duggan (“Hacksaw Ridge,” “The Great Gatsby”), composer Tom Holkenborg, sound designer Robert Mackenzie, editor Eliot Knapman, visual effects supervisor Andrew Jackson and colorist Eric Whipp. The team also includes other longtime collaborators: production designer Colin Gibson, editor Margaret Sixel, sound mixer Ben Osmo, costume designer Jenny Beavan and makeup designer Lesley Vanderwalt, each of whom won an Oscar for their work on “Mad Max: Fury Road.” 

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents, in Association with Village Roadshow Pictures, A Kennedy Miller Mitchell Production, A George Miller Film, “Furiosa.”  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on May 24, 2024 and internationally beginning on May 22, 2024.

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - HUSN (Official Video)
snippet.description:
The eleventh studio recorded single, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Husn' on all streaming platforms - https://anuvjain.lnk.to/Husn

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

Music production - Angad Bahra, PUNA
Mix and Master - Angad Bahra (Uneven studios)
Dolby Mix - Mukul Jain (Ferris Wheel Studios)
Acoustic Guitars - Harsimran Singh Bhatia

Project Managers: Madhura Rumde, Tanvi Seth

Production House: EO2 EXP
Video Producers - Risheeta and Rishabh Agrawal
Director - Pankhuri Ranjan 
Executive Producer - Farzeen Khan
Associate Producer - Ramin Yazeshani
Financial Controller - Karpu Swami
DOP - Leslie D’souza
1st AD - Malhar Wakde
DA - Smera Juneja
2nd AD - Rupali Khandelwal

Lead male actor - Tejas Ravishankar
Lead female actor - Vidushi Kaul
Production Manager -Tanvi Agarwal
Costume Stylist - Ayushi & Rajvee 
Hair & Makeup Artist - Sapna
Production Designer - Anish Pandey

Choreographer - Neeraj Lohani 

Post Producer -  Priti Rai 
Associate Post Producer - Rishabh Agarwal
Editor - Nathan Dcosta
Grade Artist - Uday Oswal

HUSN lyrics

Paragraph 1

Dekho Dekho 
Kaisi baatein yahan ki 
Hain saath par 
Hain saath na bhi
Kya itni aasaan hain?

Dekho Dekho 
Jaise mere iraaday
Waise kahaan 
Tere yahan the
Haan kitni naadan main

Chorus 1

Mere husn ke ilawa
Kabhi dil bhi maang lo na
Haye pal mein 
Main pighal jaun haan 

Ab aisa na karo 
Ke dil judna paye wapis
Teri baaton
Se bikhar jaun haan 

Paragraph 2

Mana zamana hai deewana
Isilye tune na jana 
Tere liye main 
Kaafi hoon 

Dekho Dekho 
Yeh zamane se thak kar 
Atey ho kyun masoom ban kar?
Tere liye main 
Kya hi hoon?

Chorus 2

Phir aatey kyun yahan
Karne aankhon mein 
Ho baarish?
Ab aye 
Toh theher jao na

Aur poocho na zara 
Mere din ke bare mein bhi
Bas itne mein 
Sambhal jaun haan 

Pre – Bridge

Haan ek din 
Kabhi koi 
Jab bhi padhe 
Kahani teri

Lagta mujhe
Mere naam ka 
Zikr kahin 
Bhi hoga nahin

Bridge

Haan 
Main yahin 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Dekho yeh dil ka haal kya 
Hothon se hota na bayan 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Kaisa naseeb hai mera
Milke bhi na mujhe mila 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Teri adhuri si wafa 
Maangu main maangu aur na 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Paragraph 3

Dekho Dekho
Kaisi kheenchi lakeerein
Chahe bhi dil toh bhi na jeete
Main iss daud mein nahin

Dekho Dekho 
Kaisi baatein yahan ki 
Baatein yahi dekhoon jahan bhi 
Main is daur se nahin

snippet.title: Animal Movie Telugu Review | Ranbir Kapoor | Sandeep Reddy Vanga | Bobby Deol  Ravi Telugu Traveller
snippet.description:
#animalmoviereview #animalmovie #ranbirkapoor 

Embark on a cinematic journey with Ravi Telugu Traveller as he unravels the layers of "Animal," the latest blockbuster featuring Ranbir Kapoor, directed by Sandeep Reddy Vanga, and starring Bobby Deol. In this riveting review, Ravi delves into the heart of the film, exploring the performances, direction, and narrative intricacies that make "Animal" a compelling watch. Get ready for an insightful exploration of the silver screen magic that unfolds in this must-see production.

As the curtains fall on this cinematic exploration, join me, Ravi Telugu Traveller, in the comments below to share your thoughts on "Animal." Did Kapoor's performance leave you awe-inspired? How did Vanga's direction resonate with you? Let's continue this conversation and celebrate the one-of-a-kind experience that is "Animal." Don't forget to like, subscribe, and stay tuned for more in-depth reviews on the latest releases. Until next time, happy watching!

snippet.title: BAMBOO CHICKEN | Chicken Cooking in Bamboo | Direct Fired Bamboo Chicken Recipe Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cut 4 big-sized bamboo trees to make bamboo chicken recipe. We first marinated all the chicken with masala and then put it in bamboo to cook on a direct fire. 

The bamboo chicken recipe is one of the unique and traditional recipe. It gives the chicken an awesome smell and taste while cooked by direct fire!

snippet.title: CID के सामने किसने मारी छलाँग? | CID | Unusual Investigations |28 Nov 2023 l Full Episode | सी.आई.डी
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

Team CID is called in a posh society to investigate a situation. The flat in which this incident took place was locked most of the time as per a resident. Eventually, the residents decide to break the door and enter the flat. But, when they entered the flat they were left puzzled as things normal. Later, CID starts investigating the same.

Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1494
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all episodes of 'Unusual Investigations':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIXvhXkbwjwhfRbDsJkUK3ws

snippet.title: पालक पनीर ऐसे बनायेंगे तो सब तारीफ करेंगे।Bhuna Palak Paneer Recipe। Lasooni Palak Paneer
snippet.description:
#palakpaneer #paneer #winterspecial 
Moms Palak Paneer 

INGREDIENTS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:

1 tsp Sugar 
350 Gms Palak 
3 Gree chillies 
Coriander Stems (some)
1 tsp Oil (for Grinding Palak)

For Masala 
2 Laddle Mustard Oil 
1 Inch Ginger 
5 - 6 big Garlic Cloves 
2 Onion 
3 Tomatoes 
1 tsp Jeera 
2 Tej patta 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
1 tsp Red Chilli Powder 
2 tsp Coriander Powder
1.5 Salt 
4 Tbsp Curd 
1 tsp Garam Masala 
1 tsp Kasuri Methi 
1 Tbsp Atta 
Coriander Leaves 
2 Tbsp Malai 
400 Gms Paneer

For Tadka 
2 tsp Desi ghee 
 4 Garlic Cloves (chopped)
2 dried Red Chillies 
1/2 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder

Humko Tumse Song Lyrics:
'Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge
Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Simte Huwe Se Yeh Mere Iraade
Tumko Sada Hi Chahenge
Kya Rakha Hai Aur Iss Dil Mein
Kaise Batlayenge
Dil Ko Cheer Ke Apna Dikha Dein
Tum Jo Kaho Mar Jaayenge
Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Tu Jo Kahe Toh Duniya Bhula Dein
Yeh Bhi Tu Aazma Le
Shiddat Itni Meri Wafaa Mein
Tera Bhi Dil Pighla Dein
Kya Maqsad Hai
Aur Iss Dil Ko Kitna Sataoge
Tum Na Mile To Karte Hain Wada
Phir Na Kisiko Chahenge

Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Tu Jo Na Ho Toh
Tujhse Aakhir Kaise Hum Keh Paayein
Itni Bechaini Hai Aakhir
Kaise Dil Behlaaein
Aag Lagi Hai Jo Iss Dil Mein
Kaise Hum Bujhayenge
Roshan Jo Ho Teri Duniya
Tere Liye Jal Jaayenge
Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Itni Zaalim Hai Teri Yaadein 
Haste Haste Rulaa Dein
Tujhse Kate Din
Tujhse Hi Raatein
Kaise Hum Ye Bhula Dein
Qatra Qatra Aur Iss Dil Ko Kitna Rulaoge
Tod Diya Ye Dil Jo Tumne 
Phir Bhi Tumko Chahenge

Humko tumse pyaar hai itna 
Kaise hum samjhayenge'

Episode 3942: Sundar Ka Vaada
--------------------------------------------------------
The news that Daya will finally return on Diwali has everyone at Gokuldham excited. Taarak confides in Anjali that he has a feeling that something strange will occur and that things won't go as planned. He informs Anjali that Daya Bhabhi's plan is still a mystery and that he does not believe anything Sundar says. Anjali asks him to keep quiet so as not to spoil Jetha's delight, but Tarak has already asked Jetha what's on his mind. Stay tuned!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NCC കേഡറ്റിന്റെ  കൈ അബദ്ധത്തിൽ മുഖ്യമന്ത്രിയുടെ കണ്ണിൽ കൊണ്ടപ്പോൾ
snippet.description:
മഞ്ചേരിയിൽ നവ കേരള സദസ് വേദിയിൽ മന്ത്രിമാരെ സ്വീകരിക്കുന്നതിനിടെ NCC കേഡറ്റിന്റെ  കൈ അബദ്ധത്തിൽ മുഖ്യമന്ത്രിയുടെ കണ്ണിൽ കൊണ്ടപ്പോൾ #MalayalamNewsLive #MalayalamLatestNews #MediaoneLive #MalayalamLatest #NewsMalayalam 

MediaOne is a 24x7 news channel which broadcasts the updated news from trustworthy sources. The fastest-growing channel with varied presentations makes the channel unique. So stay tuned with MediaOne for the latest updates that are happening around the world.

കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും മികച്ച വാര്‍ത്താ നെറ്റ്‌വര്‍ക്കാണ് മീഡിയവണ്‍. മൂല്യാധിഷ്ഠിതവും സ്വതന്ത്രവുമായ മാധ്യമപ്രവർത്തനം നടത്തുന്ന മലയാള ന്യൂസ് ടെലിവിഷൻ ചാനലാണിത്‌.  24 മണിക്കൂറും ലോകത്തിന്‍റെ ഏത് ഭാഗത്ത് നിന്നും ഇവിടെ തത്സമയം കാണാം. അതിവേഗം വാര്‍ത്താ വീഡിയോകള്‍ ലഭിക്കാൻ മീഡിയവണ്‍ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യാം.

മഞ്ചേരിയിൽ നവ കേരള സദസ് വേദിയിൽ മന്ത്രിമാരെ സ്വീകരിക്കുന്നതിനിടെ NCC കേഡറ്റിന്റെ  കൈ അബദ്ധത്തിൽ മുഖ്യമന്ത്രിയുടെ കണ്ണിൽ കൊണ്ടപ്പോൾ #MalayalamNewsLive #MalayalamLatestNews #MediaoneLive #MalayalamLatest #NewsMalayalam 

MediaOne is a 24x7 news channel which broadcasts the updated news from trustworthy sources. The fastest-growing channel with varied presentations makes the channel unique. So stay tuned with MediaOne for the latest updates that are happening around the world.

കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും മികച്ച വാര്‍ത്താ നെറ്റ്‌വര്‍ക്കാണ് മീഡിയവണ്‍. മൂല്യാധിഷ്ഠിതവും സ്വതന്ത്രവുമായ മാധ്യമപ്രവർത്തനം നടത്തുന്ന മലയാള ന്യൂസ് ടെലിവിഷൻ ചാനലാണിത്‌.  24 മണിക്കൂറും ലോകത്തിന്‍റെ ഏത് ഭാഗത്ത് നിന്നും ഇവിടെ തത്സമയം കാണാം. അതിവേഗം വാര്‍ത്താ വീഡിയോകള്‍ ലഭിക്കാൻ മീഡിയവണ്‍ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യാം.

snippet.title: Mujhe Khatu Bula Lijiye | Haaye Mera Dil | Dard E Dil Ki Dawa | Raj Pareek New Shyam Bhajan
snippet.description:
Mujhe Khatu Bula Lijiye | Haaye Mera Dil | Dard E Dil Ki Dawa | Raj Pareek New Shyam Bhajan

Yuki Music Presents you the most awaited bhajan of this year “Mujhe Khatu Bula Lijiye” in the melodious voice of Raj Pareek Ji. Let’s groove on the tune of Haaye Mera Dil and say this to our Lord Shyam Baba :- “Dard-E-Dil Ki Dawa Dijiye. Mujhe Khatu Bula Lijiye.”
Listen & Share with others.
Jai Shree Shyam 🙏🏼✨

Chorus

Lyrics in Hindi

[हाय मेरा दिल मेरा दिल मेरा दिल दिल

दर्द-ए-दिल की दवा दीजिए
मुझे खाटू बुला लीजिये

1. ज़ख्म दुनिया ने मुझको दिए कितने सारे
आप मरहम लगा दीजिये

2. गिर ना जाउ कहीं राह में चलते चलते
अपना दामन थमा दीजिए

3. आंसुओं के वजन से दबा जा रहा हूं
बोझ दिल का हटा दीजिये

4. हारता ही रहा जिंदगी से हमेशा
आप आकर जिता दीजिए

snippet.title: अब AARAMBH NEET 2024 का होगा AAGAAZ…… 🔥🚀 #AarambhNEET2024
snippet.description:

📲 PW App/Website: https://physicswallah.onelink.me/ZAZB/PWAppWEb

-------------------------------------------------------
Batch Description 

✏️ This batch is completely FREE for all the students aiming for NEET 2024
✏️ Will cover the complete NEET Syllabus of Physics, Chemistry, Botany & Zoology
✏️ Each Class will be LIVE on our YAKEEN YouTube Channel
✏️ 6 Days scheduled classes with ONE lecture each day
✏️ Chapterwise One Shot will be conducted with PYQ’s
✏️ The Weekly Schedule will be provided in the community post of YAKEEN’s YT Channel & Announcement Section of the PW App
✏️ Class Notes in PDF Format will be uploaded on our PW App 
✏️ Daily Practice Sheet with Text Solutions will be provided on PW App
✏️ Weekly Tests based on the Syllabus of that week will also be conducted on PW App
✏️ Classes will start from 30th November 2023

FAQ’S

Q. - Who Should Join this batch?
This batch is especially for students who are aiming for NEET 2024. 

Q. - Is This batch free or paid? 
This batch is completely FREE, you just have to click on the “BUY NOW” button, to get the free subscription.

Q. - Classes will be live or recorded?
All the lectures will be provided in LIVE format only. 

Q. - Classes will be available on YouTube or on the PW App? 
Lectures will be available on both YouTube as well as PW App. 

Q. - Where can I find the lecture notes?
You have to go to the batch section and select a particular Subject - You will find the Schedule and Lecture Notes there.

Q. - Till when can I have access to the batch?
This batch will be accessible till the NEET 2024 Exam.

snippet.title: Double Dhamaal Movie Scenes | How did Kabir become so Paisewala? | Riteish Deshmukh | Arshad Warsi
snippet.description:
How did Kabir become so Paisewala? Double Dhamaal, also known as 420s or Super Kameenas,  is a 2011 Indian Hindi-language comedy film and is directed and produced by Indra Kumar. After losing a huge sum to a police officer, four slackers find themselves unemployed and broke. They then come up on the police officer, who now apparently lives a wealthy lifestyle with his wife. They intrude in his life and blackmail him.

snippet.title: Sandeep Reddy Vanga & Bhushan Kumar Interview on Animal, Ranbir Kapoor, SRK, Prabhas, & Allu Arjun
snippet.description:
In a candid chat with Pinkvilla, Sandeep Reddy Vanga and Bhushan Kumar open up on their December 1 release, Animal starring Ranbir Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Bobby Deol and Rashmika Mandanna. The duo inform why Ranbir deserves the term superstar and label him the most versatile actor in today’s time. Sandeep confesses that it’s his dream to direct Shah Rukh Khan in a feature film, and promises a new Prabhas in Spirit. Bhushan Kumar believes that Allu Arjun’s persona will soon get a Sandeep Reddy Vanga touch, and goes back in time to inform how Ranveer Singh missed out on Kabir Singh. Sandeep terms Bhushan the best producer, whereas the latter is excited to do back-to-back films with his director. Watch this full video here!

#ranbirkapoor #animalmoviereview #pinkvilla

snippet.title: Double Dhamaal Movie Scenes | Anda-murga chod, tera toh poppat ho gaya Tony | Riteish Deshmukh
snippet.description:
Anda-murga chod, tera toh poppat ho gaya Tony. Double Dhamaal, also known as 420s or Super Kameenas,  is a 2011 Indian Hindi-language comedy film and is directed and produced by Indra Kumar. After losing a huge sum to a police officer, four slackers find themselves unemployed and broke. They then come up on the police officer, who now apparently lives a wealthy lifestyle with his wife. They intrude in his life and blackmail him.

Episode 3941: Daya Ke Aane Ki Khushi
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone at Gokuldjam is happy to learn that Daya is finally coming back on Diwali. The Gokuldham ladies are grooving in joy at the news of Daya's return. They plan to make special arrangements for Daya's welcome. Taarak tells Anjali that he feels that something weird might happen and things might not go as planned. So will Taarak's intuition be true? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3941, 29 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: PM Modi ने Uttarkashi Tunnel से बाहर निकाले जाने के बाद की मजदूरों से फोन पर बात
snippet.description:
Uttarkashi Tunnel Rescue | पीएम मोदी ने उत्तरकाशी के टनल से 41 मजदूरों को बाहर निकाले जाने के बाद उनसे फोन से बातचीत की. मोदी ने कहा कि हमारे श्रमिक भाइयों के रेस्क्यू ऑपरेशन की सफलता हर किसी को भावुक कर देने वाली है. टनल में जो साथी फंसे हुए थे, उनसे मैं कहना चाहता हूं कि आपका साहस और धैर्य हर किसी को प्रेरित कर रहा है. इसके साथ ही कहा कि मैं आप सभी की कुशलता और उत्तम स्वास्थ्य की कामना करता हूं.


PM Modi spoke to 41 laborers over phone after they were taken out from the tunnel of Uttarkashi. Modi said that the success of the rescue operation of our labor brothers is going to make everyone emotional. I want to say to the friends who were trapped in the tunnel that your courage and patience is inspiring everyone. Along with this, I wish all of you well and good health.

I want to say to the friends who were trapped in the tunnel that your courage and patience is inspiring everyone. Along with this, I wish all of you well and good health.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: "ആ 4 മാസം എനിക്കെന്ത് സംഭവിച്ചു എന്നറിയില്ല" | @AshinaAjmal169 | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalks #ashinaajmal #nevergiveup #mentalhealth
 
പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക
https://bit.ly/JoshTalksMalayalamToEnglish

ഒരാൾക്ക് എത്ര നേരം കരഞ്ഞുകൊണ്ട് മാത്രം ജീവിതം തള്ളിനീക്കാൻ കഴിയും? ഇതിനിടയിൽ കുത്തുവാക്കുകൾ കൂടി വരുമ്പോൾ, അയാളുടെ മാനസിക ആരോ​ഗ്യത്തെ വലിയ രീതിയിൽ അത് ബാധിക്കുമെന്നുറപ്പ്. നമ്മുടെ എല്ലാവരുടെയും ജീവിതത്തിൽ #mentalhealth  എത്രത്തോളം #important  ആണെന്ന് ഈ ടോക്ക് നിങ്ങളെ ഓർമിപ്പിക്കും. കാണാം  @AshinaAjmal169-ന്റെ ടോക്ക്. 

@AshinaAjmal169 shares that she initially struggled to seek help for her mental health issues. She felt ashamed and embarrassed about what she was going through and didn't want to burden others with her problems. However, as her symptoms worsened, she realized that she couldn't continue living like this and decided to seek professional help.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവയെ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഒരു സമ്മേളനമായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

localized.title: "ആ 4 മാസം എനിക്കെന്ത് സംഭവിച്ചു എന്നറിയില്ല" | @AshinaAjmal169 | Josh Talks Malayalam
localized.description:
#joshtalks #ashinaajmal #nevergiveup #mentalhealth
 
പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക
https://bit.ly/JoshTalksMalayalamToEnglish

ഒരാൾക്ക് എത്ര നേരം കരഞ്ഞുകൊണ്ട് മാത്രം ജീവിതം തള്ളിനീക്കാൻ കഴിയും? ഇതിനിടയിൽ കുത്തുവാക്കുകൾ കൂടി വരുമ്പോൾ, അയാളുടെ മാനസിക ആരോ​ഗ്യത്തെ വലിയ രീതിയിൽ അത് ബാധിക്കുമെന്നുറപ്പ്. നമ്മുടെ എല്ലാവരുടെയും ജീവിതത്തിൽ #mentalhealth  എത്രത്തോളം #important  ആണെന്ന് ഈ ടോക്ക് നിങ്ങളെ ഓർമിപ്പിക്കും. കാണാം  @AshinaAjmal169-ന്റെ ടോക്ക്. 

@AshinaAjmal169 shares that she initially struggled to seek help for her mental health issues. She felt ashamed and embarrassed about what she was going through and didn't want to burden others with her problems. However, as her symptoms worsened, she realized that she couldn't continue living like this and decided to seek professional help.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. snippet.title: मिलौना रोटी-बिहार-झारखंड स्पेशल, बिस्किट जैसी, टिफिन या यात्रा के लिये लंबी शेल्फ लाइफ । Milona Roti
snippet.description:
मिलौना रोटी, चाहे इसे पारंपरिक मिर्च-साबुत धनिया और सब्जी के साथ खायें, या चाय के साथ, बच्चों के टिफिन में रखें, या सफर में साथ में ले जायें,  लम्बी शेल्फ लाइफ वाली
#kidsfavouriterecipe #roti #teatime #traditionalrecipe 

Ingredients for Milona Roti
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 1 cup (150 grams)
बेसन - Gram flour - 1 cup (120 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/4 tsp
कलोंजी - Black cumin - 1/4 tsp
घी - Ghee - 5 tbsp 
आलू - Potato - 4 no (300 grams)
सरसों का तेल - Mustard oil - 2 tbsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
हींग - Asafoetida - 1 pinch
टमाटर - Tomato - 2 no (125 gms)
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 2 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
कशमीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1/2 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
सरसों का तेल - Mustard oil - 2 tbsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 6-7 no
धनिया - Coriander seeds - 1 tbsp
नमक - Salt
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 2-3 tbsp

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 02 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 25th November 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 02 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 25th November 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem

snippet.title: Baylagaam Episode 56 - [Eng Sub] Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 30th Nov 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Episode 56 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 30th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

Written By: Huma Hina Nafees
Directed By: Zahid Mehmood
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Trading Secrets Exposed : Stand Up Comedy by Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi (Crowd Work Video)
snippet.description:
Hello Doston,

Presenting a new Stand Up Comedy Crowd Work video 
Trading Secrets Exposed : Stand Up Comedy by Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi which was recorded in my latest comedy show called Best of GuptaJi in a stand up comedy club called Comedy County, Noida NCR. 

Why trading secrets exposed? Because in the show I met this engineer turned full time trader who is doing live trading from quite some time. In initial days he was trading like a beginners but once he gets some clients which invested some money, He started doing live trading and binary option trading also. 

This is a latest stand up comedy show called Best of GuptaJi which we have recorded in October 2023. 

Hope you enjoy this video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai and Genuinely, I am presenting my new show with an old name Best of GuptaJi which I am touring at presently.

Why Best of GuptaJi? because I want all the content in my show to be the best content from my side. So if you have seen my videos on chai, maggi, hotel, airport, tinder, starbucks etc, so you will see some amazing content which belongs to that level unique and funny. 

PLEASE NOTE : NONE OF THE YOUTUBE CONTENT WOULD BE A PART OF BEST OF GUPTAJI so Every bit of the show would be FRESH CONTENT.

snippet.title: Dr. Salunkhe ने Lab में क्यों खोला है कपड़ों की दुकान? |CID |Case Files|30 Nov 2023|Full Ep|सी.आई.डी
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

Friends are lodging in a hotel together. The following day, Anisha, one of their pals, is discovered on the road and Sagar and Mihir are discovered dead inside a hotel room. CID starts the investigation. Who is the culprit? Why do they take innocent lives? Watch the episode to know. 

Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1040
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Case Files' from CID:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIXatxtZilibD0HrpAu-9RAF
